1
00:01:16,920 --> 00:01:17,760
Yes.

2
00:01:18,440 --> 00:01:18,960
When I was young,

3
00:01:18,960 --> 00:01:20,620
I had a childhood sweetheart.

4
00:01:20,640 --> 00:01:22,170
But she was from out of town.

5
00:01:22,360 --> 00:01:24,120
She left after a few days.

6
00:01:24,680 --> 00:01:27,240
Back then, we gathered herbs on the mountain every day.

7
00:01:27,240 --> 00:01:28,500
We sold them for silver

8
00:01:28,560 --> 00:01:29,960
just to buy these snacks.

9
00:01:30,480 --> 00:01:32,080
Aren't you the Master's son?

10
00:01:32,800 --> 00:01:35,000
Why did you have to sell herbs for money?

11
00:01:37,039 --> 00:01:37,840
Oh.

12
00:01:38,240 --> 00:01:39,560
I am a concubine's son.

13
00:01:40,280 --> 00:01:41,920
So Father has never liked me.

14
00:01:42,600 --> 00:01:43,280
Oh.

15
00:01:43,680 --> 00:01:44,400
I'm sorry.

16
00:01:44,720 --> 00:01:46,039
I brought up your sad past.

17
00:01:46,039 --> 00:01:48,500
Your father really doesn't seem to like you.

18
00:01:50,520 --> 00:01:51,560
Master Shen.

19
00:01:52,560 --> 00:01:53,360
What?

20
00:01:54,160 --> 00:01:55,690
I'm just stating the truth.

21
00:01:59,880 --> 00:02:00,800
It's all right.

22
00:02:01,720 --> 00:02:03,200
My legitimate older brother

23
00:02:03,200 --> 00:02:04,930
died of illness a few years ago.

24
00:02:05,040 --> 00:02:07,280
So I am the only child left.

25
00:02:07,520 --> 00:02:09,250
Life was actually a bit better.

26
00:02:11,080 --> 00:02:12,040
But...

27
00:02:12,640 --> 00:02:15,500
My birth mother and I were driven out by the Mistress

28
00:02:15,760 --> 00:02:17,690
to live on the mountain for a while.

29
00:02:17,920 --> 00:02:20,360
Life was very bleak back then.

30
00:02:20,920 --> 00:02:22,520
It wasn't until she appeared

31
00:02:22,640 --> 00:02:24,880
that my life had some light.

32
00:02:25,760 --> 00:02:26,960
On the mountain?

33
00:02:28,520 --> 00:02:28,840
Yes.

34
00:02:29,000 --> 00:02:30,730
It was that small wooden cabin.

35
00:02:31,360 --> 00:02:32,820
I can identify these herbs

36
00:02:33,560 --> 00:02:34,920
because she taught me.

37
00:02:36,120 --> 00:02:37,640
The mountain cabin.

38
00:02:41,040 --> 00:02:42,440
Childhood sweethearts.

39
00:02:45,480 --> 00:02:48,140
I don't care if you were childhood sweethearts.

40
00:02:48,280 --> 00:02:49,520
She is my wife now.

41
00:02:49,960 --> 00:02:51,560
We have a marriage contract.

42
00:02:54,040 --> 00:02:55,240
A marriage contract?

43
00:02:55,520 --> 00:02:56,000
But...

44
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:58,520
I've never heard Doctor Ji mention this.

45
00:03:00,680 --> 00:03:01,840
We are indeed engaged.

46
00:03:01,840 --> 00:03:03,200
But since we aren't married yet,

47
00:03:03,200 --> 00:03:05,360
we don't act too intimate in public.

48
00:03:06,480 --> 00:03:08,080
On my trip to Sitai Town,

49
00:03:08,080 --> 00:03:10,200
he was entrusted by his father

50
00:03:10,200 --> 00:03:11,280
to accompany me.

51
00:03:12,760 --> 00:03:13,360
Right.

52
00:03:14,160 --> 00:03:16,320
My father asked me to ensure Ji Bai's safety.

53
00:03:16,320 --> 00:03:17,720
As for the engagement,

54
00:03:18,240 --> 00:03:19,900
it was decided by our parents.

55
00:03:21,160 --> 00:03:22,820
Naturally, we must obey them.

56
00:03:24,400 --> 00:03:25,320
I see.

57
00:03:25,480 --> 00:03:26,940
I was being presumptuous.

58
00:03:27,120 --> 00:03:27,920
It's just that

59
00:03:27,960 --> 00:03:30,160
I've never heard Doctor Ji mention it,

60
00:03:30,360 --> 00:03:31,520
so I had some doubts.

61
00:03:32,560 --> 00:03:33,920
But Brother Shen,

62
00:03:34,120 --> 00:03:36,640
what did you mean by "childhood sweethearts"

63
00:03:36,640 --> 00:03:37,840
just now?

64
00:03:39,840 --> 00:03:42,120
He took the wrong medicine recently.

65
00:03:42,280 --> 00:03:43,540
His mind is a bit fuzzy.

66
00:03:43,560 --> 00:03:44,420
Don't mind him.

67
00:03:46,360 --> 00:03:48,160
Brother Shen, Doctor Ji,

68
00:03:48,360 --> 00:03:50,490
your relationship is truly enviable.

69
00:03:50,520 --> 00:03:53,240
I hope you fulfill your engagement soon

70
00:03:53,360 --> 00:03:54,290
and tie the knot.

71
00:03:54,840 --> 00:03:57,800
I also hope Young Master Du finds his childhood sweetheart soon

72
00:03:57,800 --> 00:03:59,060
and grows old with her.

73
00:04:00,520 --> 00:04:01,120
Young Master.

74
00:04:01,120 --> 00:04:02,520
The Master is returning.

75
00:04:03,200 --> 00:04:04,000
Excuse me.

76
00:04:04,320 --> 00:04:05,360
I must take my leave.

77
00:04:05,360 --> 00:04:06,760
I must go greet my father.

78
00:04:22,520 --> 00:04:24,160
What he just said...

79
00:04:25,320 --> 00:04:28,320
sounds like the childhood friend you're looking for.

80
00:04:28,440 --> 00:04:29,970
Aren't you going to ask him?

81
00:04:32,840 --> 00:04:33,760
Follow me.

82
00:04:48,480 --> 00:04:52,340
How is your memorization of the Treatise on Cold Damage coming along?

83
00:04:53,159 --> 00:04:54,040
Huh?

84
00:04:54,760 --> 00:04:57,320
You called me here just for this?

85
00:04:58,480 --> 00:05:01,000
You are my temporary disciple now.

86
00:05:01,480 --> 00:05:04,080
Naturally, I must check on your studies.

87
00:05:08,080 --> 00:05:10,140
I am the Heir of the Prince of Zhenbei.

88
00:05:11,960 --> 00:05:13,680
My real name is not Shen Yi.

89
00:05:15,040 --> 00:05:16,240
My name is Xiao Heyan.

90
00:05:17,360 --> 00:05:19,080
During our time together,

91
00:05:19,240 --> 00:05:20,520
I figured it out.

92
00:05:24,720 --> 00:05:26,040
I'm your fiancé.

93
00:05:30,280 --> 00:05:31,960
We both ran away.

94
00:05:31,960 --> 00:05:34,240
The engagement is off.

95
00:05:35,560 --> 00:05:36,440
Besides,

96
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:38,260
you're too impulsive.

97
00:05:38,520 --> 00:05:39,850
You should go back home.

98
00:05:51,159 --> 00:05:53,800
I just can't stand seeing you with other men.

99
00:05:56,120 --> 00:05:56,800
What?

100
00:05:56,880 --> 00:05:58,440
I won't repeat myself.

101
00:06:01,920 --> 00:06:02,760
Oh.

102
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:10,840
Don't you...

103
00:06:10,840 --> 00:06:12,720
...have any questions for me?

104
00:06:14,040 --> 00:06:15,040
As long as you ask.

105
00:06:15,240 --> 00:06:16,640
I will be honest with you.

106
00:06:24,840 --> 00:06:25,640
Okay.

107
00:06:26,600 --> 00:06:27,600
Then tell me,

108
00:06:28,040 --> 00:06:30,320
what exactly happened at the Prince's Manor that day?

109
00:06:30,320 --> 00:06:32,560
Whose body was that?

110
00:06:46,000 --> 00:06:46,920
Don't drink it.

111
00:06:52,360 --> 00:06:54,220
Li Si had been by my side for years.

112
00:06:55,520 --> 00:06:57,080
He resembled me the most.

113
00:06:58,960 --> 00:06:59,960
On my wedding day,

114
00:07:00,760 --> 00:07:02,160
I wanted to get him drunk

115
00:07:02,960 --> 00:07:03,890
to stall for time

116
00:07:04,840 --> 00:07:06,500
so I could escape the wedding.

117
00:07:09,080 --> 00:07:10,880
But he ended up dying in my place.

118
00:07:19,440 --> 00:07:20,770
Stop blaming yourself.

119
00:07:21,120 --> 00:07:23,520
It won't change anything.

120
00:07:23,960 --> 00:07:25,020
He's already dead.

121
00:07:29,120 --> 00:07:30,160
What do you mean?

122
00:07:32,680 --> 00:07:33,520
Literally.

123
00:07:34,360 --> 00:07:35,690
You didn't mean to do it.

124
00:07:36,040 --> 00:07:36,800
Besides,

125
00:07:37,000 --> 00:07:41,040
the real killer is the one who wanted you dead.

126
00:07:46,920 --> 00:07:49,080
But I handed him that glass of wine.

127
00:07:50,320 --> 00:07:51,200
He is gone.

128
00:07:51,880 --> 00:07:54,040
He wanted to save you until the very end.

129
00:07:54,040 --> 00:07:55,680
You have to live on.

130
00:07:56,120 --> 00:07:58,050
Don't let his sacrifice be in vain.

131
00:07:58,120 --> 00:07:59,720
Find the real killer.

132
00:08:09,440 --> 00:08:10,800
What are you doing?

133
00:08:11,320 --> 00:08:12,720
Writing to Lord Zhenbei,

134
00:08:12,760 --> 00:08:14,680
asking him to send someone to take you back.

135
00:08:14,680 --> 00:08:15,600
I won't go back.

136
00:08:15,840 --> 00:08:17,760
I still have important business to attend to.

137
00:08:17,760 --> 00:08:19,490
Besides, Brother Li Si's death

138
00:08:19,560 --> 00:08:21,360
must have something to do with this matter.

139
00:08:21,360 --> 00:08:22,120
Nonsense.

140
00:08:22,600 --> 00:08:23,320
I have come of age.

141
00:08:23,320 --> 00:08:24,680
I'm not a child anymore.

142
00:08:24,840 --> 00:08:26,120
Why are you just like my father,

143
00:08:26,120 --> 00:08:28,380
always wanting to lock me up in the manor?

144
00:08:28,920 --> 00:08:30,850
I'm not some unmarried young lady.

145
00:08:32,120 --> 00:08:34,880
Did the Prince of Zhenbei lock you in the manor?

146
00:08:38,559 --> 00:08:40,090
It was fine when I was young.

147
00:08:40,760 --> 00:08:43,289
The older I got, the less he wanted me to go out.

148
00:08:43,520 --> 00:08:45,960
He even forbade me from going to the capital.

149
00:08:45,960 --> 00:08:48,420
I always feel like he's afraid of something.

150
00:08:51,520 --> 00:08:52,980
There are rumors outside,

151
00:08:53,240 --> 00:08:54,770
that I'm actually adopted,

152
00:08:54,920 --> 00:08:56,840
and my father never even married.

153
00:08:58,520 --> 00:09:01,360
The Princess of Zhenbei who died of illness on the battlefield

154
00:09:01,360 --> 00:09:02,800
was also made up by him.

155
00:09:16,640 --> 00:09:19,120
Even though the Prince of Zhenbei was the executioner back then,

156
00:09:19,120 --> 00:09:20,680
I don't hate him.

157
00:09:20,680 --> 00:09:22,600
He spared my son and me.

158
00:09:23,640 --> 00:09:26,000
Do you really trust him that much?

159
00:09:32,600 --> 00:09:34,400
He was a longtime friend of Shen.

160
00:09:34,640 --> 00:09:35,360
I believe

161
00:09:36,520 --> 00:09:37,640
he will agree.

162
00:09:38,960 --> 00:09:41,960
I actually have no memory of anything before I was ten.

163
00:09:42,240 --> 00:09:44,500
But I remember a place called Sitai Town,

164
00:09:44,920 --> 00:09:46,160
and the surname Shen.

165
00:09:46,960 --> 00:09:48,680
So I named myself Shen Yi.

166
00:09:49,960 --> 00:09:52,080
I came here to find my true identity.

167
00:09:53,000 --> 00:09:53,560
The Shen clan.

168
00:09:53,560 --> 00:09:54,440
I'm certain.

169
00:09:54,840 --> 00:09:56,100
I've been here before.

170
00:10:01,320 --> 00:10:03,120
This place feels very familiar.

171
00:10:03,120 --> 00:10:05,720
And this specialty cake of Sitai Town,

172
00:10:06,760 --> 00:10:08,290
the taste is also familiar.

173
00:10:08,960 --> 00:10:12,960
This is Jiujiu's favorite snack.

174
00:10:14,040 --> 00:10:15,970
Why are you looking at me like that?

175
00:10:26,400 --> 00:10:28,080
You like eating this?

176
00:10:29,280 --> 00:10:30,080
Yeah.

177
00:10:31,040 --> 00:10:32,040
It's delicious.

178
00:10:33,560 --> 00:10:35,690
I couldn't stop the first time I ate it.

179
00:11:11,920 --> 00:11:13,080
What are you doing?

180
00:11:17,400 --> 00:11:18,040
I...

181
00:11:19,680 --> 00:11:21,140
I don't think I'm injured.

182
00:11:23,360 --> 00:11:25,280
Now you are.

183
00:11:40,200 --> 00:11:40,920
In broad daylight,

184
00:11:40,920 --> 00:11:41,680
in plain view,

185
00:11:41,680 --> 00:11:42,960
we aren't married yet.

186
00:11:43,520 --> 00:11:44,720
How could you do this?

187
00:11:58,960 --> 00:12:00,760
What's wrong?

188
00:12:13,520 --> 00:12:15,560
You should go back.

189
00:12:15,880 --> 00:12:18,520
It's dangerous to be out alone.

190
00:12:19,600 --> 00:12:21,960
You're so unguarded.

191
00:12:23,600 --> 00:12:24,860
I'm worried about you.

192
00:12:25,960 --> 00:12:27,690
My martial arts are excellent.

193
00:12:28,040 --> 00:12:29,440
It was only because of you

194
00:12:29,880 --> 00:12:31,210
that I let my guard down.

195
00:12:33,000 --> 00:12:34,880
So what if you're skilled?

196
00:12:35,240 --> 00:12:37,560
Danger is everywhere.

197
00:12:37,560 --> 00:12:40,600
Anything can happen in the martial world.

198
00:12:40,600 --> 00:12:42,360
You never know what might happen next.

199
00:12:42,360 --> 00:12:43,440
Don't worry.

200
00:12:43,480 --> 00:12:44,880
I won't die with you here.

201
00:12:45,040 --> 00:12:46,570
Besides, I can protect you.

202
00:13:28,160 --> 00:13:28,840
Yi, Yi, Nan.

203
00:13:28,840 --> 00:13:29,080
Yi, Yi, Nan.

204
00:13:29,080 --> 00:13:30,280
Wu, Zhang, Li, Zheng, Chen, Luo, Deng.

205
00:13:29,520 --> 00:13:30,280
Yi, Yi, Nan.

206
00:13:57,960 --> 00:13:58,920
Ma, Miao, Lu, Ran.

207
00:13:58,920 --> 00:13:59,920
Ma, Miao, Lu, Ran.

208
00:14:03,320 --> 00:14:04,600
Lyu, Sun, Zhang, Meng.

209
00:14:04,800 --> 00:14:05,660
Pan, Xiu, Long.

210
00:14:04,800 --> 00:14:05,280
Lyu, Sun, Zhang, Meng.

211
00:14:08,200 --> 00:14:09,040
Xu.
